{"tid":2222930,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"恆大爆煲，要香港埋單","createTime":"2020-09-29T12:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T21:20:56.000Z","uid":100276,"like":179,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"3690714950b92b54afb694e26b41009a308e2aa8","tid":2222930,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:07:42.000Z","msg":"恒大 （03333） 發公告指，近日與持有恆大地產總額 1300億（人民幣，下同）的戰略投資者進行商談，並於今日與持有恆大地產總額863億的戰略投資者簽訂補充協議，補充協議明確戰略投資者已同意不要求進行回購並繼續持有恆大地產權益，且在恒大地產的股權比例保持不變。<br />\n<br />\n恒大又指，已與持有恆大地產總額155億人民幣的戰略投資者商談完畢，該等戰略投資者正在辦理審批手續，而其餘282億戰投正在商談中。<br />\n<br />\n這意味恒大不需要於2021年1月31前履行1300億元的投資回購義務。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0hksXQY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0hksXQY.png&h=6c8676d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強逼債轉股，<br />\n係香港用股票套現埋單"},{"pid":"e8998b289836e488246f94c1061b8b53205298b3","tid":2222930,"uid":220309,"like":160,"dislike":2,"score":158,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"好事黎，死都係死班藍絲愛國廢老"},{"pid":"e057127395843b75b6df20d3ce84b61ccf97b33d","tid":2222930,"uid":5178,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"班友幾開心"},{"pid":"4b9e612d718d962f379aadc90da679cc2cfd7e49","tid":2222930,"uid":1086,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"香港政府可唔可以援助一下國內企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57a570f3da40840b7ef6b0a8352b8844521eb4a","tid":2222930,"uid":55335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:43:33.000Z","msg":"MPF"},{"pid":"762cb809dbeb06093b8f4973e31cb31481e24d37","tid":2222930,"uid":59570,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T13:20:37.000Z","msg":"繼續，個泡煲得愈大，資金鏈斷裂爆得愈勁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原本恆大一間，而家拉多幾間落呢個無底洞<br />\n<br />\n將親中資一網吸盡<img src=\"/a